g/resource/Javelin_throw\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 344}, {\"ngram\": \"his limited eyesight\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 430}, {\"ngram\": \"the world record\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"atParis2024\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 480}, {\"ngram\": \"a remarkable journey\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 511}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympic champion\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pembroke has battled deteriorating vision - and the threat of going completely blind - for most of his life after being diagnosed with retinitis pigmentosa aged just six.\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 729, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 559, \"end\": 567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Parish\", \"score\": 0.9982871729587195, \"rank\": 0.001713717571900456, \"text\": \"Pembroke\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Parish\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Parish\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"deteriorating vision\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 600}, {\"ngram\": \"the threat\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 617}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"retinitis pigmentosa\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The genetic disorder affects the retina and has left the 33-year-old with only 10 per cent vision.\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The genetic disorder\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 751}, {\"ngram\": \"the retina\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"only 10 per cent vision\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite his impairment, Pembroke was poised to represent Great Britain at the London 2012 Olympics before a snapped elbow ligament ruined that dream and caused him to reassess his priorities.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 1022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 855, \"end\": 863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Parish\", \"score\": 0.9982871729587195, \"rank\": 0.001713717571900456, \"text\": \"Pembroke\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Parish\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Parish\"}, {\"begin\": 888, \"end\": 901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.6651715020238935, \"rank\": 0.4974153259196947, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 909, \"end\": 929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.178822826101231e-16, \"text\": \"London 2012 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his impairment\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"a snapped elbow ligament\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 961}, {\"ngram\": \"that dream\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"his priorities\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1021}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He embarked on a four-and-a-half-year sabbatical to see the world while he still could and then returned to win F13 gold as a Para athlete atTokyo2020.\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a four-and-a-half-year sabbatical\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1072}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"F13 gold\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1144}, {\"ngram\": \"a Para athlete\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd grown up with this thing in the back of my mind going, 'I am going to lose my eyesight when I am mid-20s',\\\" Pembroke told the PA news agency ahead of his second Paralympics.\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1355, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this thing\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1206}, {\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1218}, {\"ngram\": \"my mind\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1229}, {\"ngram\": \"my eyesight\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1268}, {\"ngram\": \"mid-20s\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1286}, {\"ngram\": \"Pembroke\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"the PA news agency\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1322}, {\"ngram\": \"his second Paralympics\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been deteriorating since I was born.\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There are certain interventions that are coming about now and I am actually part of a trial in my right eye.\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"certain interventions\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1482}, {\"ngram\": \"a trial\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"my right eye\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They injected gene therapy into the back of the eye and it has stabilised the condition so far, which has been amazing.\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1632, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gene therapy\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1553}, {\"ngram\": \"the eye\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"the condition\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Hopefully they can do the other eye now because it was part of a trial.\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1706, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the other eye\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"a trial\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1705}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe I will not lose my eyesight in its entirety.\\\"\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1758, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my eyesight\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1740}, {\"ngram\": \"its entirety\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spotting migrating humpback whales from cliffs in north-westernAustraliaand meeting wife Martina in Sardinia were among the highlights of Pembroke's \\\"very awesome adventure\\\", which also included time in New Zealand and south-east Asia.\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1860, \"end\": 1868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sardinia\", \"score\": 0.9963460431634122, \"rank\": 0.0032267094547936844, \"text\": \"Sardinia\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sardinia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sardinia\"}, {\"begin\": 1898, \"end\": 1906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Parish\", \"score\": 0.9982871729587195, \"rank\": 0.001713717571900456, \"text\": \"Pembroke\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Parish\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Parish\"}, {\"begin\": 1963, \"end\": 1974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9390508219434854, \"rank\": 0.05888305645209488, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"humpback whales\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"cliffs\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1806}, {\"ngram\": \"north-westernAustraliaand meeting wife Martina\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"the highlights\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1894}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1959}, {\"ngram\": \"south-east Asia\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He only had a year to train for Tokyo but topped the podium amid a torrential downpour thanks to a Games-record throw of 69.52 metres.\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2029, \"end\": 2034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999837785291331, \"rank\": 1.568922876058034e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a year\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2015}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2056}, {\"ngram\": \"a torrential downpour thanks\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2090}, {\"ngram\": \"a Games-record throw\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2114}, {\"ngram\": \"69.52 metres\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have never seen rain like it,\\\" said Pembroke.\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2172, \"end\": 2180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Parish\", \"score\": 0.9982871729587195, \"rank\": 0.001713717571900456, \"text\": \"Pembroke\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Parish\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Parish\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rain\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was like Armageddon.\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2206, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2195, \"end\": 2205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armageddon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.340167739615388e-15, \"text\": \"Armageddon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armageddon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armageddon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking back on it now, when I was competing as an able-bodied athlete, my eyesight was bad enough then to compete in the category that I am in and since that point it's actually got worse.\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2398, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an able-bodied athlete\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2279}, {\"ngram\": \"my eyesight\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"the category\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2339}, {\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Maybe if I'd found Para sport earlier, I would not have gone travelling and done all of those things.\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Para sport\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2430}, {\"ngram\": \"those things\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I got diagnosed with the condition, what that instilled into me is that if I want to do things with my eyesight, I should do them now because who knows when my vision will go.\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the condition\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2544}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2604}, {\"ngram\": \"my eyesight\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2621}, {\"ngram\": \"my vision\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2676}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's acted like a catalyst for me to do the things I want to do in life.\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2760, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a catalyst\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2714}, {\"ngram\": \"the things\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2738}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sometimes it really gets me down.\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2796, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(But) as much as it takes away, it gives, I find.\\\"\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2847, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pembroke, from Hereford, last year claimed the world title in Paris before retaining it in May inKobe, Japan.\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2958, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2864, \"end\": 2872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hereford\", \"score\": 0.9999996768202049, \"rank\": 2.821025007829852e-07, \"text\": \"Hereford\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hereford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hereford\"}, {\"begin\": 2911, \"end\": 2916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997914024097, \"rank\": 2.0859759818185186e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pembroke\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2857}, {\"ngram\": \"the world title\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 2907}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 2940, \"to\": 2943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He returns to the French capital with ambitions of breaking the world record of 71.01m to keep hold of his Paralympic crown.\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 3084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2978, \"end\": 2984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.45710583134322835, \"rank\": 0.7194327383231675, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ambitions\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3007}, {\"ngram\": \"the world record\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3036}, {\"ngram\": \"hold\", \"from\": 3055, \"to\": 3059}, {\"ngram\": \"his Paralympic crown\", \"from\": 3063, \"to\": 3083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am so close to it,\\\" said Pembroke, who has a tattoo of an eye containing the Agitos symbol and the words 'RP (retinitis pigmentosa) made me fly' on his right bicep to commemorate his maiden Paralympic success.\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3114, \"end\": 3122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Parish\", \"score\": 0.9982871729587195, \"rank\": 0.001713717571900456, \"text\": \"Pembroke\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Parish\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pembroke_Parish\"}, {\"begin\": 3166, \"end\": 3172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_symbols\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Agitos\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_symbols\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_symbols\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an eye\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3150}, {\"ngram\": \"his right bicep\", \"from\": 3237, \"to\": 3252}, {\"ngram\": \"his maiden Paralympic success\", \"from\": 3268, \"to\": 3297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Last year, I was 51 centimetres away from it, which was so frustrating.\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3372, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully in Paris, I am going to crack it.\", \"from\": 3373, \"to\": 3416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3386, \"end\": 3391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997914024097, \"rank\": 2.0859759818185186e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone's going there to beat me.\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3453, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do feel that pressure sometimes but I do feel as though I thrive on that pressure and if anything it just makes me throw further.\\\"\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3586, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that pressure\", \"from\": 3464, \"to\": 3477}, {\"ngram\": \"that pressure\", \"from\": 3524, \"to\": 3537}, {\"ngram\": \"if anything\", \"from\": 3542, \"to\": 3553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the page\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3611}, {\"ngram\": \"another page\", \"from\": 3627, \"to\": 3639}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 3643, \"to\": 3651}, {\"ngram\": \"inPlease\", \"fr